headline.print_headline: Marlins Beat Reds 2-1 on Yelich's Hit in 10th
headline.main: Marlins Beat Reds 2-1 on Yelich's Hit in 10th

lead_paragraph: Christian Yelich's RBI single in the bottom of the 10th inning lifted the Miami Marlins to a 2-1 victory over the Cincinnati Reds on Saturday night.
